</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="DE7592D89A7BFFF0316CFF5FA3FAFF33" author="Hu, S. J. &amp; Condamine, F. L. &amp; Monastyrskii, A. L. &amp; Cotton, A. M." box="[1138,1198,189,215]" pageId="11" pageNumber="228" pagination="286 - 300" refId="ref5868" refString="Hu, S. J., Condamine, F. L., Monastyrskii, A. L. &amp; Cotton, A. M. (2019) A new species of the Graphium (Pazala) mandarinus Group from Central Vietnam (Lepidoptera: Papilionidae). Zootaxa, 4554 (1), 286 - 300. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4554.1.10" type="journal article" year="2019">2019</bibRefCitation>
